# Table

---

The table component makes information easier to compare and scan for users.

## When to use this component
Use the table component to let users to compare information in rows and columns.

## When not to use this component
Never use the table component to layout content on a page. Instead, use the components for this, for example text+photo.


> Note to DS team: This might need defining! What other layout components is there to help creating layouts?
